---
// File: src/pages/about.astro
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About | Stacksolver UK"
  description="Stacksolver UK Limited — independent Cyber Security, AI Engineering and Compliance consultancy based in Brighton. Lean delivery for UK, EU and US regulated industries."
>
  <section class="bg-white dark:bg-black">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-24">
      <p class="text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-olive-600 dark:text-olive-400 mb-6">About</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-8">
        A British boutique<br />with a clear specialty.
      </h1>

      <div class="space-y-5 text-lg text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          Stacksolver UK Limited is a Brighton-based consultancy.
          <strong>Cyber security is our specialty</strong> — and the rest of what we do, from AI engineering
          to governance, risk and compliance, is built around it.
        </p>
        <p>
          We were founded on a simple premise: that mid-market UK firms deserve <strong>senior expertise
          delivered without the overhead of a Big 4 engagement</strong>. We operate with a lean core team
          and a curated bench of independent specialists, engaged on a per-project basis. No bench warmers,
          no junior staff billed at senior rates, no rotating account managers.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What we do -->
  <section class="bg-zinc-50 dark:bg-zinc-950 border-t border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-20">
      <p class="text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-olive-600 dark:text-olive-400 mb-4">What we do</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-8">
        Cyber as our core. Five practices around it.
      </h2>

      <ul class="space-y-4 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 text-base leading-relaxed">
        <li><strong class="text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">Cyber Security</strong> — Cyber Essentials Plus, penetration testing, vCISO, incident response.</li>
        <li><strong class="text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">AI Engineering</strong> — sovereign AI in your perimeter, ethical by default, ISO 42001 ready.</li>
        <li><strong class="text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">Areas + AI</strong> — Procurement + AI and HR + AI as our anchor practices. AI embedded in the function.</li>
        <li><strong class="text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">Governance &amp; Compliance</strong> — vCISO retainer, risk register, DPO-as-a-Service, internal audit.</li>
        <li><strong class="text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">ISO &amp; Compliance Frameworks</strong> — ISO 27001, ISO 42001, ISO 27701, ISO 22301, SOC 2, GDPR.</li>
        <li><strong class="text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">NIS2 · DORA · Supply Chain Risk</strong> — for UK firms with European operations.</li>
        <li><strong class="text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">AI Security &amp; Red Teaming</strong> — adversarial testing of LLMs and AI applications.</li>
        <li><strong class="text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">Local AI Stack</strong> — sovereign deployments on Apple Silicon, NVIDIA or private cloud.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Who we work with -->
  <section class="bg-white dark:bg-black border-t border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-20">
      <p class="text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-olive-600 dark:text-olive-400 mb-4">Who we work with</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-8">
        Built for regulated industries.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
        We focus on five sectors where audit trails, regulatory pressure and data sovereignty are not
        optional: <strong>Technology</strong>, <strong>Professional Services</strong>,
        <strong>Financial Services</strong>, <strong>Healthcare</strong> and <strong>Corporate Services</strong>.
      </p>
      <p class="text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        We serve clients across the United Kingdom, the European Union and the United States.
        Our clients are typically mid-market organisations — large enough to need real GRC and AI
        capability, small enough that Big 4 pricing is not viable.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our standards -->
  <section class="bg-zinc-50 dark:bg-zinc-950 border-t border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-20">
      <p class="text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-olive-600 dark:text-olive-400 mb-4">Our standards</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-8">
        We hold ourselves to what we ask of others.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Stacksolver UK is registered with Companies House (No. 16227080), aligned with
        ISO 27001:2022 controls, and committed to the principles of the Modern Slavery Act 2015,
        the Bribery Act 2010 and the Equality Act 2010. Our Cyber Essentials Plus certification
        is in progress, and our ICO registration is being finalised.
      </p>
      <p class="text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        All of our public policies, statements and frameworks are available in our
        <a href="/trust" class="text-olive-600 dark:text-olive-400 hover:underline">Trust Center</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-white dark:bg-black border-t border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 text-center">
      <p class="text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        For commercial enquiries please email
        <a href="mailto:hello@foxfifth.com" class="text-olive-600 dark:text-olive-400 hover:underline">hello@foxfifth.com</a>
        or use the contact form. We reply within two working days.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-olive-500 text-zinc-900 font-semibold border border-olive-500 hover:bg-olive-600 transition-colors">
          Contact us <span aria-hidden>→</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/method" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-transparent text-zinc-900 dark:text-white font-medium border border-olive-500 hover:bg-olive-500/10 transition-colors">
          How we work
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
